{
  "stem": "7094.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the job was very tough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anything connected with fashion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I really didn't qualify for any of it, because in the store, I used to do interior designing, lighting, and china and glass.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have any qualifications.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But instinct, common sense, and applying yourself-- at that time it was easy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, you need qualification.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that time, you could-- you could do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so the job, in the last 10 years of my career, was traveling to the Far East.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, again, my curiosity came to the front, because most businessmen go from airport to the office and back, but I used to combine it with 10 days' holiday-- a week and weekend.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I went-- I had the opportunity of traveling, maybe in a very superficial way, but nonetheless coming in contact with different cultures, different religion.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went to Japan and China and India and Malaysia and Australia in a sort of very superficial way, but it does give you a glimpse of a different-- you know, we sort of think Europe is the center of the world.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There is a Far East, which is developing very quickly and very well and very-- the Chinese are very intelligent people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Japanese.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a little bit of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when I reached 60, I decided that I have time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did my calculation, and I said, I can live on my-- what I have.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wanted to have a little bit of leisure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's the first time in my life that I wanted to have some leisure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before that, in my period from '72 to '86, I was very involved in the community.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was president of B'nai B'rith, involved in WIZO and Ladies' Guild, all these usual commitments.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
